# Secrets for provider auth are not read from flat env vars by this codebase.
# Provider credentials (mwps and any other providers) go into provider_clients
# in the adapter config (per-provider auth.api_key); commercial LLM access
# itself is delegated to the external model-access-core server.
#
# This file is a placeholder should host-level secrets ever be needed again.
# Ensure secrets.env is in .gitignore.
